# --- MacOS Junk ---
# When you open a folder on a Mac, it creates this hidden file
# to remember icon positions. We DON'T want this in our code.
.DS_Store

# --- VS Code Settings ---
# VS Code creates a folder for your local settings.
# Your settings (blue theme) might annoy me (dark theme), so we ignore them.
.vscode/

# --- Terraform State (Future Proofing) ---
# Terraform stores sensitive data (IPs, passwords) in state files.
# NEVER commit these to GitHub.
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup

# --- Logs ---
# If a script crashes and dumps a log file, we don't want it.
*.log